    <span class="msep">◇</span>
    <span>Ijazah holders</span>
    <span class="msep">◇</span>
    <span>Tajweed certified</span>
    <span class="msep">◇</span>
    <span>Women only platform</span>
    <span class="msep">◇</span>
    <span>Seven stage process</span>
    <span class="msep">◇</span>
    <span>One on one sessions</span>
    <span class="msep">◇</span>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="story" id="story">
  <div class="container story__inner">
    <div class="section-num">01</div>
    <div class="story__head">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Who we are</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">A platform built for women who want to learn the Quran properly.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="story__body">
      <p>
        Laha Space was started for one reason. Too many women begin learning the Quran online, land with a teacher they never quite trusted, and quietly stop showing up. We wanted that to change.
      </p>
      <p>
        So we built a small, careful platform where every teacher is a woman, holds real qualifications, and has been personally interviewed, tested and reviewed by our team before she ever appears here.
      </p>
      <p class="story__signature">— The Laha Space team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="story__image-wrap">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585036156171-384164a8c675?w=900&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop&crop=center"
        alt="Woman reading Quran"
        class="story__image"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <div class="story__image-grain" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="vetting" id="vetting">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="vetting__head">
      <div class="section-num">02</div>
      <div>
        <span class="section-eyebrow">How we choose our teachers</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Seven stages.<br/><em>No shortcuts.</em></h2>
        <p class="section-desc">
          Every teacher you see here has passed through our full vetting process. Here is exactly what that means.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <ol class="stages">
      <li class="stage" data-aos="fade-up">
        <span class="stage__num">01</span>
        <div class="stage__body">
          <h4>Application</h4>
          <p>The teacher submits a detailed application covering her qualifications, ijazah, teaching experience and references.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="stage__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </li>
      <li class="stage" data-aos="fade-up">
        <span class="stage__num">02</span>
        <div class="stage__body">
          <h4>Initial screening</h4>
          <p>Our team reviews every document and qualification before anything moves forward.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="stage__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </li>
      <li class="stage" data-aos="fade-up">
        <span class="stage__num">03</span>
        <div class="stage__body">
          <h4>One on one interview</h4>
          <p>A personal conversation to understand her background, her approach and her values as a teacher.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="stage__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </li>
      <li class="stage" data-aos="fade-up">
        <span class="stage__num">04</span>
        <div class="stage__body">
          <h4>Interview review</h4>
          <p>The team evaluates every interview note carefully before proceeding to the teaching test.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="stage__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </li>
      <li class="stage" data-aos="fade-up">
        <span class="stage__num">05</span>
        <div class="stage__body">
          <h4>Teaching test</h4>
          <p>The teacher delivers a live teaching demonstration observed and reviewed by our team.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="stage__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </li>
      <li class="stage" data-aos="fade-up">
        <span class="stage__num">06</span>
        <div class="stage__body">
          <h4>Training program</h4>
          <p>Accepted teachers complete our internal onboarding and training before being listed publicly.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="stage__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </li>
      <li class="stage stage--final" data-aos="fade-up">
        <span class="stage__num">07</span>
        <div class="stage__body">
          <h4>Fully vetted <span class="stage__pill">live</span></h4>
          <p>Only now does the teacher appear on Laha Space. Every teacher you see here is here for a reason.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="stage__arrow stage__arrow--check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="teachers-section" id="teachers">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="teachers-section__head">
      <div class="section-num">03</div>
      <div>
        <span class="section-eyebrow">Our teachers</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Meet the community.</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Browse our vetted teachers and book a free discovery session with the one that feels right for you.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="teacher-filters" data-aos="fade-up">
      <button class="filter-btn filter-btn--active" data-category="all">All teachers</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-category="tajweed">Tajweed</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-category="memorization">Memorization</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-category="beginner">Beginner</button>
    </div>

    <div class="teacher-grid" id="teacherGrid">
      <div class="grid-loading">
        <div class="grid-loading__dot"></div>
        <div class="grid-loading__dot"></div>
        <div class="grid-loading__dot"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="apply-cta" data-aos="fade-up">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="apply-cta__inner">
      <div class="apply-cta__content">
        <div class="section-num section-num--light">04</div>
        <span class="section-eyebrow section-eyebrow--light">Are you a teacher?</span>
        <h2 class="apply-cta__title">
          Join a community<br/>
          <em>of vetted teachers.</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="apply-cta__desc">
          If you hold an ijazah or have verified qualifications and are passionate about teaching the Quran to women, we would love to read your application.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="apply-cta__action">
        <a href="/apply" class="pill pill--light pill--lg">
          <span>Apply to teach</span>
          <span class="pill__arrow" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
        </a>
        <span class="apply-cta__hint">No fee, no commission.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="modal-overlay" id="teacherModal" hidden>
  <div class="modal">
    <button class="modal__close" id="modalClose" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
    <div class="modal__body" id="modalBody"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal-overlay" id="bookingModal" hidden>
  <div class="modal modal--booking">
    <button class="modal__close" id="bookingModalClose" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
    <div class="modal__body" id="bookingModalBody"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/public-foot') %>
